(define/contract (maximum-length s)
  (-> string? exact-integer?)
  (let ([n (string-length s)])
    (let loop ([len (quotient n 3)])
      (if (= len 0) -1
          (let check ([start 0] [found #f])
            (if (or found (> (+ start (* 3 len)) n))
                (if found len (loop (- len 1)))
                (let ([sub (substring s start (+ start len))])
                  (let loop2 ([i (+ start 1)])
                    (if (> (+ i (* 2 len)) n)
                        (check (+ start 1) found)
                        (if (string=? sub (substring s i (+ i len)))
                            (if (string=? sub (substring s (+ i len) (+ i (* 2 len))))
                                (check (+ start 1) #t)
                                (loop2 (+ i 1)))
                            (loop2 (+ i 1))))))))))))
